    cpu_map: Add TSX_CTRL bit for IA32_ARCH_CAPABILITIES MSR
    
    CVE-2019-11135
    
    When TSX_CTRL bit of IA32_ARCH_CAPABILITIES MSR is set to 1, the CPU
    supports IA32_TSX_CTRL MSR which can be used to disable and/or mask TSX.
    
